      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'You are a ghost hunter and have been hired to investigate an old manor,
    but upon entering the grounds the ghosts locked the gates behind you!


    Look
    around for clues on how to appease the ghosts and find your way into the manor,
    maybe once they are all happy they will let you out.


    [TAB] - Opens your
    codex, there you can revisit your clues and find more information about the manor.

    [F]
    - Turns on your flashlight.'
